    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Truth
---
Spiritual truth should not be sold, lest the seller be injured spiritually.
You lose any spiritual contact the moment you commercialize it. Those who
have the truth would not be packaging it and selling it, so anyone who is
selling it really does not possess it.
